if ! Reprompt_Message
    s
        emphasis(level="moderate")
            prosody(volume="loud") You initiated to pay, 
        break(time="20ms")
        prosody(volume="loud") 
            prosody(rate="slow")  $#{Amount} 
        emphasis(level="moderate") to your 
            prosody(volume="loud") 
                prosody(rate="slow") #{SZPayee}.
        break(time="20ms")
        emphasis(level="moderate") To authorise this transaction, 
        prosody(rate="slow") spell the received OTP, from your registered mobile number.
else 
    s
        emphasis(level="moderate")
                prosody(volume="loud") Anything else?